Improved Evasion		KEY:xxx ~ 				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:xxx Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 9th level, a monk's evasion ability improves. She still takes no damage on a successful Reflex saving throw against attacks such as a dragon's breath weapon, but henceforth she takes only half damage on a failed save. A helpless monk (such as one who is unconscious or paralyzed) does not gain the benefit of improved evasion.
