Silent Magic		KEY:xxx ~ 				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:xxx Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:The white mage can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Silent Spell feat. This does not increase the MP cost or the level of the spell.
