Aura of Disruption		KEY:xxx ~ 				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:xxx Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:This aura causes enemies to take a penalty on all Concentration checks. A caster must still make a Concentration check to cast defensively even if the caster is not within threatened reach or the spell is lost and the MP is spent.
Aura of Elemental Resistance		KEY:xxx ~ 				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:xxx Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:This aura grants the sword saint and nearby allies to gain an elemental (all) resistance.
